-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusDownloaded 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusDownloaded

iOS 7.0+iPadOS 7.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.9+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusDownloaded: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemdownloadingstatusdownloaded#Discussion)

A string used as the value for [`NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey`](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitempercentuploadedkey) to indicate that there is a local version of this item available.

The most current version will be downloaded as soon as possible.
